# Total War: Shogun 2, with Flydigi Apex 2 in mind.

JoyXY wasd deadzone 40 # Move camera
# |Alt+W| Fire Broadside Forward
# |Alt+A| Fire Broadside Left
# |Alt+D| Fire Broadside Right

CamXY Mouse 100 # Move Cursor
mousecalibration 1000

TriggerR M1 # Select
BumperR M2 # Move
BumperL Shift # Modifier

PinkyLeft Ctrl # Modifier
PinkyRight M3 # Zoom To Mouse
PaddleRight Alt # Formations
PaddleLeft Space # Toggle Character Movement Speed

TriggerL layer 1 # More Groups
Left layer 2 # Selections
Down layer 3 # Modes
Up layer 4 # Pings
Right layer 5 # Map Mode Menus
MenuL Tab
MenuR Escape # Main Menu

layer 1 # Camera Controls
MenuL O # Toggle Radar Visibility
ActionH Home # Zoom to and Select General
ActionV End # Zoom to Unit
ActionA N # Intelligent Zoom
ActionB H # Toggle First-Person Mode
ActionC Delete # Toggle Tracking
ActionD Insert # Context Camera
