layer 2 # Selections
ActionH ! Ctrl M # Select All Missile Units / Auto-Merge Units
ActionV ! Ctrl I # Select All Melee Units
ActionA ! Ctrl C # Select All Cavalry Units
ActionB ! Ctrl B # Select All Siege Weapon Units
ActionC ! Ctrl . # Select Next
ActionD , # Select Previous

layer 3 # Modes
ActionH [ # Increase Rank | Decrease Sail
ActionV ] # Increase File | Increase Sail
ActionA R # Toggle Run | Repair Buildings / Ships
ActionB B # Toggle Boarding
ActionC F # Toggle Melee Mode
ActionD ! Ctrl P # Disband Selection
BumperL BackSlash # Step Unit/Group Backwards
BumperR BackQuote # Step Unit/Group Forwarrds | Sail Forward

layer 4 # Pings
ActionH F5 # Standard Ping
ActionV F6 # Move Ping
ActionA F7 # Attack Ping
ActionB F8 # Defend Ping
ActionC Backspace # Cancel order
ActionD Enter # Deselect All / End Turn

layer 5 # Map Mode Menus
ActionH K # Show Diplomatic Relations
ActionV L # Rotate Unit / Group Left | Show Clan Management Panel
ActionB ; # Rotate Unit / Group Right
ActionA M # Toggle Battle UI | Show Mastery of the Arts Panel
ActionC N # Show Finance Panel
ActionD O # Toggle Radar Visbility

